  <body>
    <main>

      <!-- ── HERO ── -->
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-inner">
          <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>Nadya Post</h1>
            <p class="tagline">Doctor. Engineer. Founder.</p>
          </div>
          <img src="/nadya.png" alt="Nadya Post" class="hero-photo" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr />

      <!-- ── MY STORY ── -->
      <section>
        <div class="container">
          <p class="label">My Story</p>
          <p>I've felt what it's like to be dismissed by a doctor.</p>
          <p>Not taken seriously. Told your symptoms are "normal." Sent away without answers.</p>
          <p>I trained as a medical doctor in Russia, then spent years doing cancer surgery research in Oslo. I saw first-hand how patients' real problems get handled, and how often they don't. Then I joined the tech industry, and the contrast was impossible to ignore. Software teams ship solutions in weeks. Healthcare moves in decades.</p>
          <p>I'm living this myself right now. I'm approaching pre-menopause, and my GP looks at my blood results and tells me everything is fine. It doesn't feel fine. Being dismissed when you know something is off. That's the specific thing I want to fix.</p>
          <p>I want better care for women in Australia going through hormonal transition. That's what I'm building.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr />

      <!-- ── BACKGROUND & CREDENTIALS ── -->
      <section>
        <div class="container">
          <p class="label">Background &amp; Credentials</p>
          <div class="cred-stack">
            <div class="cred-block">
              <p class="cred-title">Medical Training</p>
              <p>MD, Moscow State University of Medicine and Dentistry</p>
              <p>Research Fellow, Oslo University Hospital,<br />Interventional Center, Department of Hepatic Surgery</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cred-block cred-block--second">
              <p class="cred-title">Engineering &amp; Leadership</p>
              <p>Engineering Manager, Xero (2021–2026)</p>
              <p>Payroll on Mobile, scaled across four countries and three platforms</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="publications">
            <p class="label" style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">Published Research</p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24308605/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  Margin status after laparoscopic resection of colorectal liver metastases
                </a>
                <span class="pub-meta">HPB (Oxford), 2014 · First author</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26496309/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  Inflammatory Response After Laparoscopic Versus Open Resection, Oslo-CoMet Trial
                </a>
                <span class="pub-meta">Medicine (Baltimore), 2015</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25055544/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  Russian classification of complications in surgery
                </a>
                <span class="pub-meta">Vestnik Khirurgii, 2014</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr />

      <!-- ── WHAT I'M BUILDING ── -->
      <section>
        <div class="container">
          <p class="label">What I'm Building</p>
          <p>
            I'm co-founding <a href="https://meridhealth.com.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Merid Health</strong></a>, Australia's first bulk-billed telehealth platform for women's health, starting with menopause care.
          </p>
          <p>
            Seven million Australian women live with menopause symptoms. Most wait years for answers. Most pay hundreds out of pocket for care that should be accessible to everyone.
          </p>
          <p>We're changing that.</p>
          <p class="social-links">
            Follow my journey:
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/nadyapost/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>
            <span class="dot">·</span>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nadya-post-33ab6b63/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

